          |__| W I R E L E S S   F R E E D O M
 -----------------------------------------------------


1) git remote add upstream https://github.com/openwrt/openwrt.git
2) git fetch upstream
3) git checkout master
4) git merge upstream/master ( If your local branch didn't have any unique commits, Git will instead perform a "fast-forward" )
5) git checkout -b newbranch


